headline: On Semiconductor (ON) Acquires Vcore Tech to Strengthen AI Power Management Portfolio
summary: On Semiconductor Corporation (NASDAQ:ON) ranks among the best cheap semiconductor stocks to buy. On September 23, On Semiconductor Corporation (NASDAQ:ON) announced that it had agreed on a deal to acquire the rights to Vcore power technologies and its related intellectual property licensing from Aura Semiconductor. headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock with Exciting Potential and 2 We Question
summary: Generating cash is essential for any business, but not all cash-rich companies are great investments. Some produce plenty of cash but fail to allocate it effectively, leading to missed opportunities.
